  "profileFieldsSaveFailed": "Account created, but optional profile fields (date of birth, gender, blood type) couldn't be saved. You can edit them later in መገለጫ > አርትዕ መገለጫ.",
  "privacyPolicyTitle": "ግላዊነት Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Last updated: March 2025",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your privacy is paramount. ይህ ግላዊነት Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related ውሂብ. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Data Collection",
  "privacyDataCollectionBody": "We collect the following categories of ውሂብ: • Personal Information: ስም, email address, phone number, date of birth, and gender. • ጤና Data: ደም type, allergies, chronic conditions, medications, vital signs, symptom logs, and triage results. • አደጋ Contacts: Names, phone numbers, and relationships of your designated contacts. • Device Data: Device type, operating system, and app version for compatibility and support. • Usage Data: Feature interactions and anonymized analytics to improve our services. We only collect ውሂብ that is necessary for providing our health companion services. You have full control over what መረጃ you provide.",
  "privacySectionDataStorage": "2. Data Storage & Encryption",
  "privacyDataStorageBody": "Your ውሂብ is stored using industry-leading security measures: • Encryption at Rest: ሁሉም ውሂብ stored in our databases is encrypted using AES-256 encryption. • Encryption in Transit: ሁሉም ውሂብ transmitted between your device and our servers uses TLS 1.3 encryption. • ጤና ፓስፖርት: Your health passport ውሂብ is encrypted with a unique key derived from your credentials. • QR Code Sharing: Shared health ውሂብ via QR codes is encrypted and time-limited. • Infrastructure: Our servers are hosted in SOC 2 አይነት II certified ውሂብ centers with 24/7 monitoring. We do አይደለም store payment card መረጃ. ሁሉም payment processing is handled by certified third-party providers.",
  "privacySectionGdpr": "3. GDPR Compliance",
  "privacyGdprBody": "{appName} is fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR): • Lawful Basis: We process your ውሂብ based on your explicit consent and contractual necessity. • Data Minimization: We only collect and process ውሂብ that is strictly necessary. • Purpose Limitation: Your ውሂብ is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. • Right to Access: You can request a complete copy of your personal ውሂብ at any time. • Right to Rectification: You can update or correct your ውሂብ through the app settings. • Right to Erasure: You can request complete deletion of your account and ውሂብ. • Right to Portability: You can export your ውሂብ in a machine-readable format. • Data Processing Agreements: ሁሉም third-party processors have signed DPAs. • Cross-Border Transfers: Data is processed within the EU/EEA unless explicit consent is given otherwise.",
  "privacySectionYourRights": "4. Your Rights",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your ውሂብ: • Access: View all your personal and health ውሂብ within the app or request a ውሂብ export. • Correction: አርትዕ your profile መረጃ at any time through አርትዕ መገለጫ. • Deletion: Request account deletion through ቅንብሮች > Data & ግላዊነት > ሰርዝ Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain ውሂብ is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific ውሂብ processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any time without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app support feature.",
  "privacySectionContactUs": "5. አግኙ Us",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns about this ግላዊነት Policy or our ውሂብ practices, please contact us: • ኢሜል: privacy@vitalseker.com • ድጋፍ: support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to all privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
